%% Data Science Pipelines - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Dashboard
    participant API as ml-pipeline API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP, 8887/TCP gRPC
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Tekton as Tekton Controller
    participant Driver as Driver Container<br/>(V2 DAG Orchestration)
    participant Launcher as Launcher Container<br/>(V2 Step Execution)
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO Object Store<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata gRPC<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432 TCP
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant SWC as ScheduledWorkflow Controller
    participant Cache as Cache Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User, DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Execution (V2 Tekton Backend)
    User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    API->>DB: Store run metadata
    API->>K8s: Create PipelineRun CR<br/>TLS, SA Token
    K8s->>Tekton: PipelineRun reconciliation
    Tekton->>Driver: Start DAG orchestration
    Driver->>K8s: Create TaskRun CRs<br/>TLS, SA Token
    Tekton->>Launcher: Start step execution
    Launcher->>S3: Upload/Download artifacts<br/>HTTPS, Access Key
    Launcher->>MLMD: Log metadata & lineage<br/>gRPC, No Auth

    Note over PA, DB: Flow 2: Persistence Agent Sync
    PA->>K8s: Watch Workflow/PipelineRun CRs<br/>TLS, SA Token
    K8s-->>PA: Workflow status updates
    PA->>API: Report run status<br/>HTTP/gRPC, SA Token
    API->>DB: Update run status

    Note over SWC, API: Flow 3: Scheduled Workflow Execution
    SWC->>K8s: Watch ScheduledWorkflow CRs<br/>TLS, SA Token
    K8s-->>SWC: ScheduledWorkflow events
    SWC->>K8s: Create Workflow/PipelineRun<br/>TLS, SA Token
    SWC->>API: Report run creation<br/>HTTP/gRPC, SA Token

    Note over K8s, Cache: Flow 4: Cache Check (Mutating Webhook)
    K8s->>Cache: Pod admission review<br/>HTTPS/TLS, mTLS
    Cache->>DB: Check cache entry<br/>Optional TLS, User/Pass
    DB-->>Cache: Cache result
    Cache-->>K8s: Mutated pod spec<br/>(cached result or pass-through)
